 story, I couldn't believe the things that her mother said, that I wanted to yell at her myself so she could open her eyes to what she kept saying.Again, this book deals with some real issues and emotions that it made me feel like the story was inspired by true events. It is amazing that Holly and Stacey co-wrote a book so emotionally charged, that had me wanting to know what was going to happen next at every turn of a page. Awesome job ladies!", "overall": 5.0, "summary": "A Heartfelt Story of Loss, Love and a Second Chance at Love and Life with a Special Someone", "unixReviewTime": 1405900800, "reviewTime": "07 21, 2014"}
